Optimize content across all product pages, category pages, and key landing pages for search engines and users. Implement comprehensive meta tags, structured headings, alt text for images, and enhanced product descriptions for all 137 products.

**Success looks like:**

- All 137 product pages have unique, optimized meta titles and descriptions
- All product images have descriptive alt text
- H1, H2, H3 heading structure implemented site-wide
- Product descriptions enhanced with keyword-rich, user-focused content
- Category pages have optimized content and meta tags
- Homepage and key landing pages optimized
- Schema markup for products verified and enhanced
- All content changes logged and tracked in PROGRESS.md

