### Step 6: Enhance Product Descriptions

1. Review current product descriptions:
    - Assess length, quality, keyword usage
    - Identify products with missing or weak descriptions
2. Define description enhancement strategy:
    - Minimum length: 150-200 words per product (if feasible)
    - Include: Fabric details, design features, occasion suitability, care tips
    - Natural keyword integration (fabric type, saree type, design elements)
3. Implementation options:
    - Option A: Enhance descriptions directly in Supabase (if you have content ready)
    - Option B: Create a process/template for future enhancement
    - Option C: Prioritize top 20-30 products for immediate enhancement
4. For this phase, focus on:
    - Ensuring all products have at least a short_description (from Supabase)
    - Displaying descriptions on product pages with proper formatting
    - Logging which products need manual content enhancement post-migration
5. Log to PROGRESS.md:
    - "Product descriptions: [X products have descriptions, Y need enhancement]"
    - "Description display: [Implemented / Issues]"
    - "Content enhancement plan: [Documented for post-Phase-2 work]"

